ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-young-adults-diagnosis-screening-treatment-signs-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Colon%20cancer%20cases%20in%20young%20adults%20are%20rising.%20Josh%20Herting%2C%2034%2C%20shared%20his%20story%20so%20people%20know%20the%20signs%20and%20symptoms%20and%20when%20to%20get%20checked%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-young-adults-diagnosis-screening-treatment-signs-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20wedding%20on%20ice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bride%20and%20groom%20in%20an%20ice%20cave%20in%20Iceland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a9b87a3d2714887886e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnn%20Peters%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Iceland%20Wedding%20Planner%2C%20specializes%20in%20crafting%20%26quot%3Bexperience-driven%26quot%3B%20weddings%20and%20elopements.%3Cp%3EAnn%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJemma%20Schofield%20gathered%20the%20layers%20of%20tulle%20from%20her%20wedding%20dress%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20held%20a%20rope%20in%20the%20other.%20Her%20olive-green%20Wellington%20boots%20splashed%20in%20the%20frigid%20glacial%20runoff%20as%20she%20spelunked%20into%20the%20venue%20for%20her%20big%20day%3A%20an%20ice%20cave%20along%20Iceland's%20southern%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchofield%20and%20her%20now-husband%2C%20Chris%20Watson%2C%20always%20dreamed%20of%20getting%20married%20in%20Iceland.%20As%20dairy%20farmers%20from%20Lancashire%2C%20UK%2C%20they've%20rarely%20been%20able%20to%20leave%20the%20cows%20for%20extended%20periods%20to%20travel%20together.%20Still%2C%20they%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20different%2C%20an%20adventure%2C%26quot%3B%20Schofield%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20bride%2C%20particularly%2C%20had%20her%20heart%20set%20on%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20do%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20ice%20cave%20despite%20their%20June%20wedding%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20Icelandic%20fairy%20godmother%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnn%20Peters%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ficelandweddingplanner.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIceland%20Wedding%20Planner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20specializes%20in%20crafting%20%26quot%3Bexperience-driven%26quot%3B%20weddings%20and%20elopements.%20Her%20events%20grant%20exclusive%20access%20to%20hidden%20gems%20or%20off-the-grid%20locations%20throughout%20Iceland%20thanks%20to%20her%20resourceful%20scouting%2C%20relationships%20with%20private%20landowners%2C%20and%20a%20team%20of%20expert%20guides.%20As%20an%20entrepreneur%20catering%20to%20the%20growing%20experience%20economy%2C%20in%20which%20meaningful%20memories%20are%20valued%20over%20luxe%20products%2C%20no%20request%20is%20too%20outlandish%2C%20no%20detail%20too%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-guest-costs-money-diary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eattended%20countless%20weddings%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-photos-photography-contest-winners-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewritten%20about%20them%20for%20years%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20lifestyle%20correspondent%2C%20and%20even%20officiated%20a%20few.%20I%20thought%20I'd%20seen%20everything.%20Then%20I%20spent%20a%20day%20with%20Peters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ice-cave%20wedding%20inside%20a%20glacier%20%E2%80%94%20in%20June%3F%20Consider%20the%20wish%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ann%20Peters%20(right)%20positions%20bride%20Jemma%20Schofield%20and%20groom%20Chris%20Watson%20for%20photos%20ahead%20of%20their%20ice-cave%20wedding%20ceremony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b75f7a3d271488789227%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeters%2C%20right%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Iceland%20Wedding%20Planner%2C%20is%20a%20wedding%20planner%20and%20photographer.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGlaciers%20were%20part%20of%20what%20drew%20Peters%20to%20Iceland%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Originally%20from%20Ohio%2C%20she%20traveled%20to%20Iceland%20in%202010%20to%20climb%2040%20glaciers%20before%20turning%2040%2C%20which%20she%20exceeded%20before%20her%20milestone%20birthday%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20Iceland%20that%20she%20homed%20in%20on%20her%20entrepreneurial%20vision%20for%20experience-driven%20weddings%2C%20combining%20her%20love%20of%20daring%20travel%2C%20eye%20for%20wedding%20photography%2C%20and%20logistics%20background%20to%20launch%20Iceland%20Wedding%20Planner%20in%202012.%20After%20commuting%20back%20and%20forth%20for%20three%20years%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Iceland%20in%202015%2C%20where%20she%20now%20resides%20full-time%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20three%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20say%20that%20'experience-driven'%20means%20that%20it%20touches%20your%20five%20senses%2C%26quot%3B%20Peters%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20people%20to%20get%20goosebumps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeters%20was%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve.%20In%20an%20Eventbrite%20poll%2C%20over%2078%25%20of%20surveyed%20millennials%2C%20America's%20largest%20generation%20by%20population%20with%20over%20%241.3%20trillion%20in%20annual%20consumer%20spending%2C%20said%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcook-chef-manager-amusement-parks-gen-z-attendant-experience-economy2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epreferred%20experiences%20over%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20November%2C%20BI%20named%20the%20growing%20%26quot%3Bexperience%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20centered%20on%20leisure%2C%20hospitality%2C%20and%20recreation%2C%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-trends-fueling-great-careers-include-infrastructure-experiential-and-artificial-intelligence-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E5%20trends%20to%20bet%20your%20career%20on%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20As%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Z%20prioritize%20spending%20on%20experiences%20over%20tangible%20items%2C%20they're%20driving%20the%20demand%20for%20premium%20services%20such%20as%20Iceland%20Wedding%20Planner%2C%20where%20prices%20range%20from%20%2415%2C000%20elopements%20to%20%2465%2C000%20luxe%20events%20for%2050%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20worst%20nightmare%20is%20to%20end%20up%20getting%20a%20bride%20that's%20spent%20%2425%2C000%20on%20her%20dress%20and%20says%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20it%20wet.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20it%20dirty%2C'%26quot%3B%20Peters%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20work%20in%20our%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20their%20wedding%2C%20Peters%20met%20with%20Schofield%20and%20Watson%20in%20the%20lobby%20of%20Hotel%20V%C3%ADk%2C%20a%20sleek%2C%20charcoal-gray%20building%20set%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Icelandic%20town's%20mossy%20cliffs%20and%20black-sand%20beaches.%20After%20Peters%20went%20over%20the%20itinerary%2C%20the%20couple%20told%20me%20more%20about%20their%20love%20story%2C%20which%20began%20when%20they%20were%20schoolmates%20at%2010%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20in%20love%20with%20him%20it's%20not%20even%20funny%2C%26quot%3B%20Schofield%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20my%20grandma%20and%20granddad%20I%20was%20going%20to%20marry%20this%20boy%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20remember%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20going%20their%20separate%20ways%2C%20they%20reconnected%20in%20their%2020s%20when%20Watson%20walked%20into%20a%20bar%20where%20Schofield%20worked%20as%20a%20bartender.%20As%20Schofield%20told%20it%2C%20she%20went%20home%20with%20him%20and%20never%20left%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifteen%20years%20later%2C%20their%20ice-cave%20wedding%20marked%20the%20next%20step%20in%20their%20adventure%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20back%20on%20our%20wedding%20day%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20remember%20it%20as%20the%20best%20experience%20we've%20ever%20had%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20share%20the%20adventure%20with%20our%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20couple%20told%20Peters%20in%20a%20questionnaire%20during%20the%20wedding%20planning%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bride%20and%20groom%20walking%20on%20a%20glacier%20in%20Iceland%20wearing%20crampons%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b69e43bb77284ba4784b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bride%20and%20groom%20wore%20ice-climbing%20gear.%3Cp%3EAnn%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20walked%20outside%20at%207%20a.m.%20the%20next%20day%20and%20saw%20an%20enormous%20Super%20Jeep%20with%20tires%20that%20reached%20my%20neck%2C%20waiting%20to%20whisk%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20off%20to%20the%20secret%20ice%20cave%2C%20I%20knew%20this%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20weddings%20I'd%20ever%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20Peters%20outside%20the%20hotel%20sipping%20a%20Red%20Bull%20and%20taking%20photographs%20of%20the%20wedding%20dress%2C%20rings%2C%20and%20other%20accouterments%20as%20the%20couple%20ate%20breakfast.%20The%20strong%20Icelandic%20winds%20whipped%20her%20pink-streaked%20hair%20as%20she%20grabbed%20a%20few%20rocks%20to%20keep%20the%20hem%20of%20Schofield's%20dress%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20boarded%20the%20Super%20Jeep%2C%20which%20is%20more%20accurately%20described%20as%20a%20monster%20truck.%20A%20pickup%20truck%20towed%20a%20trailer%20with%20a%20portable%20bathroom%20since%20the%20secluded%2C%20scenic%20locations%20we%20were%20headed%20to%20didn't%20have%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20picked%20up%20the%20wedding%20officiant%2C%20a%20local%20pastor%20dressed%20in%20hiking%20boots%20and%20an%20Icelandic%20wool%20sweater%2C%20just%20outside%20town.%20Then%2C%20we%20began%20driving%20off-road%20out%20into%20the%20wilderness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moss-covered%20mountains%20in%20Iceland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3bf9c7a3d2714887899a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeters%20grants%20exclusive%20access%20to%20remote%20locations%20throughout%20Iceland.%3Cp%3EAnn%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20driver%20Dav%C3%AD%C3%B0%20Geir%20J%C3%B3nasson%2C%20told%20us%20about%20the%20local%20geology%20and%20Icelandic%20folklore%20as%20he%20nonchalantly%20maneuvered%20over%20boulders%20and%20sinkholes.%20It%20immediately%20became%20clear%20why%20the%20average%20tourist%20in%20an%20SUV%20wouldn't%20stand%20a%20chance%20on%20these%20rugged%20routes.%20There%20was%20no%20cellphone%20reception%2C%20and%20the%20ride%20was%20so%20bumpy%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20an%20astronaut%20training%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20protect%20her%20trade%20secrets%2C%20Peters%20was%20adamant%20that%20I%20not%20reveal%20any%20identifying%20details%20about%20the%20locations%20we%20visited.%20Before%20she%20allowed%20me%20to%20crash%20Schofield%20and%20Watson's%20wedding%20for%20this%20story%2C%20I%20signed%20a%20nondisclosure%20agreement%2C%20switched%20off%20my%20phone's%20GPS%20capabilities%2C%20and%20agreed%20not%20to%20photograph%20any%20landmarks%20that%20could%20give%20away%20our%20whereabouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20those%20beautiful%20locations%20to%20look%20as%20amazing%20as%20they%20do%20on%20their%20wedding%20day%20as%20when%20they%20come%20back%2025%20years%20from%20now%20to%20renew%20those%20vows%2C%26quot%3B%20Peters%20told%20me%20about%20operating%20with%20such%20secrecy.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20don't%20want%20people%20to%20get%20into%20hairy%20situations.%20Because%2095%25%20of%20our%20locations%20are%20only%20accessible%20via%20Super%20Jeep%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20anyone%20with%20just%20a%20regular%20SUV%20trying%20to%20venture%20in%20and%20get%20stuck%20in%20a%20glacier%2C%20river%2C%20and%20quicksand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20locations%20were%20so%20remote%20that%20I%20couldn't%20reveal%20them%20even%20if%20I%20wanted%20to.%20How%20would%20I%20begin%20to%20give%20directions%3F%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BKeep%20driving%20on%20unmarked%2C%20rocky%20terrain%20and%20take%20a%20right%20at%20the%20third%20sinkhole.%20If%20you%20reach%20a%20bottomless%20cliff%2C%20you've%20gone%20too%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20driving%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20we%20arrived%20in%20a%20valley%20surrounded%20by%20moss-covered%20mountains.%20Ours%20were%20the%20only%20tire%20tracks%20for%20miles.%20Peters%20and%20her%20crew%20of%20mountaineers%20unloaded%20the%20supplies%3A%20ropes%2C%20waders%2C%20crampons%2C%20and%20lighting%20for%20photos.%20Then%2C%20the%20bride%2C%20groom%2C%20and%20Iceland%20Wedding%20Planner%20team%20began%20the%2020-minute%20hike%20up%20to%20the%20glacier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20ice%20cave%2C%20Schofield%20and%20Watson%20accessorized%20their%20wedding%20outfits%20with%20rubber%20boots%20and%20crampons%20and%20giggled%20as%20they%20clipped%20each%20other's%20helmets%20under%20their%20chins.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Peters%20scampered%20up%20and%20over%20the%20cave%20to%20ensure%20everything%20was%20in%20order%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20Crew%20members%20set%20up%20lights%20and%20ropes%20along%20the%20glacier's%20icy%20walls%20to%20facilitate%20the%20climb%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ice%20cave%20in%20Iceland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b8ac6fcb546d2d4d09f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20walls%20of%20the%20ice%20cave.%3Cp%3EAnn%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESchofield%20entered%20first%2C%20followed%20by%20Watson.%20The%20rippled%20ice%2C%20smooth%20from%20the%20flowing%20water%2C%20glittered%20in%20the%20darkness.%20The%20walls%20reflected%20sapphire-blue%20light%20where%20the%20sun%20hit%20them%2C%20creating%20a%20magnificent%20cathedral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bride%20and%20groom%20stood%20on%20a%20mound%20of%20black%20volcanic%20sand%20with%20the%20hollow%20swirl%20of%20the%20cavern%20behind%20them.%20As%20Peters%20positioned%20her%20camera%2C%20the%20pastor%20began%20to%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20was%20entirely%20inaudible%20over%20the%20cave's%20gushing%20river%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20matter.%20Schofield%20and%20Watson%20were%20the%20only%20two%20people%20in%20the%20world%2C%20it%20seemed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20first%20kiss%20as%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%20Peters%20handed%20them%20a%20small%20bottle%20of%20Icelandic%20moonshine%20for%20a%20celebratory%20swig.%20Wearing%20waterproof%20waders%20with%20her%20camera%20in%20hand%2C%20she%20crouched%20down%20in%20the%20icy%20water%20to%20capture%20the%20perfect%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJune%202%20was%20a%20rare%20sunny%20day%20in%20Iceland.%20At%20our%20next%20stop%2C%20a%20giant%20waterfall%20in%20another%20undisclosed%20location%2C%20powerful%20streams%20of%20water%20glistened%20as%20they%20tumbled%20down%20the%20cliff.%20The%20glacial%20runoff%20was%20so%20pure%20that%20we%20could%20drink%20directly%20from%20the%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20waterfall%2C%20Peters%20and%20another%20crew%20member%20laid%20out%20a%20colorful%20spread%20of%20macarons%2C%20fruit%2C%20and%20sparkling%20wine%20on%20a%20bed%20of%20decorative%20blankets%20and%20pillows.%20The%20others%20hung%20back%20as%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20arrived%20at%20their%20feast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20taken%20me%20places%20I've%20never%20seen%2C%20and%20I'm%20an%20Icelander%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20crew%20member%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Watson%20and%20Jemma%20Schofield%20on%20their%20wedding%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3c24f7a3d271488789b26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWatson%20and%20Schofield%20on%20their%20wedding%20day.%3Cp%3EAnn%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20more%20scenic%20stops%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20the%20hotel%20in%20V%C3%ADk%20at%20dusk%2C%20where%20dinner%20awaited%20the%20newlyweds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20them%20whether%20their%20wedding%20day%20was%20everything%20they%20had%20hoped%20it%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20wetter%2C%26quot%3B%20Watson%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20loved%20every%20minute%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Schofield%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECovered%20in%20dirt%20and%20utterly%20spent%20after%20the%2012-hour%20whirlwind%20wedding%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20collapse%20into%20bed.%20Peters%2C%20however%2C%20looked%20ready%20to%20climb%20another%20glacier%2C%20not%20one%20pink-streaked%20hair%20out%20of%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ficeland-ice-wedding-glacier-extreme-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707562561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3ab177a3d271488788978%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ficeland-ice-wedding-glacier-extreme-2024-2%22%2