20of%20disorientation%20or%20seasickness%20being%20inside%20the%20windowless%20room.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20hallway%20with%20the%20closet%20and%20desk%20with%20a%20hair%20dryer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a2ce6fcb546d2d4cf757%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20room%20came%20with%20a%20few%20outlets%20and%20a%20hair%20dryer.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20get%20seasick%2C%20but%20I%20luckily%20didn't%20feel%20any%20nausea%20on%20this%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20have%20trouble%20with%20my%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20either.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20port%20was%20called%20Taino%20Bay.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd28317a3d27148877335d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Caribbean's%20bigger%20Explorer%20of%20the%20Seas%20blocks%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky%20in%20this%20photo.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pitch-black%20room%20put%20me%20right%20to%20sleep%20at%20night%20and%20kept%20me%20asleep%20until%20my%20alarm%20went%20off%20around%207%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20I%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20every%20morning%2C%20and%20during%20the%20winter%2C%20that%20means%20getting%20up%20before%20sunrise.%20So%2C%20forcing%20myself%20awake%20without%20sunlight%20wasn't%20anything%20different%20from%20my%20regular%20day-to-day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20fact%2C%20I%20sleep%20better%20than%20I%20had%20in%20weeks%2C%20thanks%20to%20my%20dark%20and%20cozy%20little%20nook.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20the%20TV%20on%20with%20a%20channel%20guide.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a5596fcb546d2d4cf93f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV%20was%20small%20but%20had%20information%20on%20things%20like%20de-embarkation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20movies.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20the%20dark-out%20room%20help%20me%20sleep%20through%20the%20night%2C%20but%20I%20was%20also%20able%20to%20nap%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20even%20if%20the%20lack%20of%20sunlight%20did%20bother%20me%2C%20I%20didn't%20spend%20enough%20time%20in%20my%20stateroom%20to%20justify%20the%20pricey%20upgrade.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author's%20book%20and%20Heineken%20beer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd15676fcb546d2d4b9b45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnboard%2C%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20reading%20in%20the%20lounge%2C%20playing%20trivia%2C%20or%20watching%20shows.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20the%20allure%20of%20cruises%20is%20exploring%20the%20giant%20ship%20and%20enjoying%20the%20entertainment%2C%20so%20an%20additional%20%24150%20for%20a%20porthole%20cabin%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20more%20for%20a%20balcony%20or%20better%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20make%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20only%20went%20to%20my%20cabin%20to%20sleep%2C%20shower%2C%20and%20change%2C%20so%20I'd%20rather%20use%20the%20extra%20cash%20on%20activities%20instead%20of%20my%20accommodation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pool%20deck%20on%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1d3243bb77284ba30fa5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pool%20deck%20on%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%