ntiated%2C%20the%20driver's%20account%20is%20deactivated.%26quot%3B%20The%20spokesperson%20also%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.walmart.com%2Fcontent%2Fcorporate%2Fen_us%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Fdelivering-a-world-class-experience-on-the-spark-driver-platform.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteps%20it%20has%20taken%20to%20address%20bots%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20several%20teams%20dedicated%20to%20preventing%20any%20illicit%20or%20fraudulent%20third-party%20apps%20from%20violating%20our%20terms%20of%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Instacart%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20which%20have%20successfully%20blocked%20access%20to%20these%20sorts%20of%20services.%20%26quot%3BAny%20shopper%20found%20to%20be%20engaging%20in%20fraudulent%20activity%20or%20otherwise%20violating%20their%20contract%20will%20be%20removed%20from%20our%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoorDash's%20policy%20%26quot%3Bexplicitly%20prohibits%20Dashers%20from%20sharing%20their%20account%20information%20with%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20including%20third%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DoorDash%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20found%20violating%20our%20rules%20faces%20removal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20Para%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20bots%20than%20Para's%20exist%2C%20including%20for%20specific%20apps.%20One%20called%20%26quot%3BSpark%20Ninjas%26quot%3B%20supposedly%20captures%20orders%20automatically%20on%20Walmart's%20Spark%20delivery%20platform.%20Subscribers%20can%20tell%20the%20bot%20which%20orders%20to%20take%20based%20on%20the%20expected%20payout%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsparkninjas.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20website.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Spark%20Ninja%20didn't%20respond%20to%20messages%20or%20a%20call%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBots%20are%20undermining%20the%20true%20gig%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20can%20rip%20off%20workers%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBots%20aren't%20unique%20to%20gig%20work%20apps%2C%20with%20similar%20codes%20being%20used%20to%20grab%20top-selling%20products%20on%20apps%20and%20websites%20for%20years.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsneaker-bots-how-to-buy-make-and-run-the-tech-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esneaker%20resellers%20use%20bots%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20snap%20up%20pairs%20of%20shoes%20from%20limited-edition%20drops%20by%20brands%20like%20Nike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-making-snkrs-app-fairer-fighting-bots-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENike%20has%20responded%20by%20improving%20its%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20coming%20up%20with%20new%20ways%20to%20make%20sure%20customers%20themselves%20have%20a%20fair%20shot%20at%20getting%20the%20sneakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBots%20are%20also%20used%20to%20create%20fake%20accounts%20at%20banks%20in%20order%20to%20move%20money%20illicitly%2C%20Sharell%20Barshishat%2C%20a%20senior%20threat%20analyst%20at%20security%20and%20anti-fraud%20consultancy%20BioCatch%2C%20told%20BI.%20The%20use%20of%20bots%20on%20apps%20like%20Spark%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20extension%20of%20technology%20used%20against%20banks%20and%20retailers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20this%20true%20gig%20economy%20that's%20kind%20of%20spreading%20out%20this%20opportunity%20for%20everybody%2C%20you're%20more%20so%20giving%20it%20to%20these%20few%20people%20who%20have%20access%20to%20these%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20Barshishat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBots%20appear%20to%20be%20just%20one%20way%20that%20some%20gig%20workers%20are%20improving%20their%20earnings.%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20other%20social%20media%20sites%20have%20had%20postings%20that%20offer%20to%20sell%20driver%20accounts%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-accounts-go-for-hundreds-dollars-social-media-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprospective%20gig%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%2C%20BI%20reported%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20workers%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-app-multiple-accounts-names-verify-identity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart's%20Spark%20delivery%20program%20appear%20to%20be%20using%20multiple%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pick%20up%2C%20shop%2C%20and%20deliver%20orders%20under%20names%20other%20than%20their%20own%2C%20BI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20also%20a%20risk%20of%20workers%20getting%20ripped%20off.%20One%20Texas-based%20driver%20for%20Spark%20said%20he%20traded%20Telegram%20messages%20with%20someone%20who%20claimed%20to%20sell%20bots%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bot%20literally%20grabs%20all%20the%20high-paying%20orders%20in%20your%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20on%20the%20other%20end%20told%20him%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20of%20the%20conversation%20shared%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20days%20after%20the%20driver%20sent%20the%20person%20behind%20the%20account%20about%20%241%2C000%20worth%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20he%20still%20had%20no%20bot.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20just%20a%20scammer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20driver%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20a%20gig%20delivery%20app%20like%20Instacart%2C%20DoorDash%2C%20or%20Walmart%20Spark%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-workers-using-bots-claim-orders-delivery-apps-doordash-spark-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707561722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e5bd14ca513d8242dd89a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%