er.com%2Flong-haul-flights-not-worth-it-shorter-trips-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20getting%20a%20hydrating%20facial%2C%20blasting%20your%20favorite%20songs%20in%20a%20retro%20arcade%2C%20and%20lounging%20among%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20reality%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fchase-sapphire-lounge-laguardia-airport-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChase%20Sapphire%20Lounge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20exclusive%20airport%20club%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-chase-sapphire-lounge-us-boston-reserve-credit-card-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20credit-card%20company%20launched%20a%20new%20location%20in%20NYC's%20LaGuardia%20Airport%20(LGA)%20on%20January%2016%2C%20followed%20by%20another%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fchase-sapphire-lounge-nyc-jfk-airport-new-york-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohn%20F.%20Kennedy%20International%20Airport%20(JFK)%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20a%20week%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.chase.com%2Fnews%2Fchase-sapphire-lounge-by-the-club-at-lga%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20company's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20credit-card%20companies%20making%20airport%20lounges%20far%20more%20accessible%20than%20they%20once%20were%20for%20those%20willing%20to%20hold%20a%20premium%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-travel-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Lounge%20is%20free%20and%20unlimited%20for%20%24550-per-year%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20credit%20cardholders%2C%20wh