E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20one%20cab%20ride%20and%20one%20TSA%20checkpoint%2C%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Lounge%20inside%20LaGuardia%20Airport's%20Terminal%20B.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20a%20blue-mirrored%20entrance%20to%20an%20airport%20lounge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b91f357a3d27148875ce0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20the%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Lounge%20at%20LaGuardia%20Airport%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Lounge%20is%20past%20security%20in%20LaGuardia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.panynj.gov%2Fport-authority%2Fen%2Fpress-room%2Fpress-release-archives%2F2023-press-releases%2Flaguardia-terminal-b-named-world-s-best-new-airport-terminal-bas.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520addition%2520to%2520the%25205%2CNYC%2520%2526%2520Company%2520Foundation%2527s%2520Visionaries%2520and%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive-star%3C%2Fa%3E%20Terminal%20B%2C%20home%20to%20various%20airlines%2C%20including%20American%2C%20JetBlue%2C%20Southwest%2C%20United%2C%20and%20Air%20Canada%2C%20as%20Tzielekis%20told%20BI.%20The%20lounge%20is%20open%20from%204%3A30%20a.m.%20to%209%3A30%20p.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20terminal%2C%20I%20headed%20up%20to%20the%20fourth%20floor%20to%20the%20lounge's%20entrance.%20From%20there%2C%20I%20walked%20down%20a%20long%20hallway%20and%20took%20an%20elevator%20down%20to%20the%20lounge's%20first%20floor%2C%20where%20the%20welcome%20desk%20was%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20walking%20into%20a%20high-end%20hotel.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dark%20and%20good%20walls%20with%20gold%20finishings%20in%20front%20of%20the%20lounge's%20welcome%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b91fa7ac2de4f17ee5d1bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lounge's%20welcome%20desk.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20inside%20the%20lounge%2C%20I%20marveled%20at%20the%20modern%20finishings%20and%20large%2C%20framed%20local%20artwork%20as%20guests%20checked%20in%20as%20early%20as%20three%20hours%20before%20their%20upcoming%20flights%2C%20showing%20their%20Priority%20Pass%2C%20credit%20card%2C%20and%20boarding%20pass%20for%20complimentary%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPast%20the%20welcome%20desk%20was%20a%20two-story%20space%20full%20of%20refreshments%2C%20plants%2C%20and%20comfy%20seating.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20a%20lounge%20with%20seveeral%20seating%20areas%20and%20hanging%20plants%20from%20a%20mezzanine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b91fe043bb77284ba1b2b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20peek%20inside%20the%20lounge's%20first%20floor.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20for%20the%20informative%20flight%20screens%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20forget%20I%20was%20in%20an%20airport%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two-story%20space%20was%20tastefully%20laid%20out%20with%20modern%2C%20comfortable%20couches%20and%20cushy%20chairs.%20Even%20on%20a%20Friday%20morning%2C%20there%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20places%20to%20sit%20%E2%80%94%20unlike%20a%20gate%20before%20boarding%2C%20where%20I%20sometimes%20find%20myself%20squatting%20on%20the%20floor%20as%20passengers%20pack%20the%20limited%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immediately%20noticed%20that%20the%20lighting%20in%20the%20space%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20there%20were%20windows%20in%20the%20lo