ed%20on%20the%20design%20of%20tennis%20sneakers%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efrom%20brands%20such%20as%20Veja%2C%20Common%20Projects%2C%20and%20Nisolo%20or%20Adidas%20Stan%20Smiths%2C%20Gazelle%2C%20and%20Samba%20are%20great%20options%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20enough%20to%20only%20wear%20the%20right%20shoes%2C%20there's%20a%20level%20of%20upkeep%20to%20keep%20them%20looking%20presentable.%20Teich%20recommends%20taking%20dress%20shoes%20to%20the%20cobbler%20if%20they%20need%20a%20repair%20or%20a%20polish%2C%20and%20investing%20in%20a%20magic%20eraser%20or%20a%20shoe%20cleaner%20for%20sneakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20to%20revive%20tired%20sneakers%20is%20by%20switching%20the%20laces%20or%20bleaching%20them%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Play%20around%20with%20accessories%2C%20details%2C%20and%20color%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maree%20Ellard%20styled%20in%20a%20corporate%20outfit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4a957917a1dae02446449%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221035%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaree%20Ellard%20styled%20in%20a%20corporate%20outfit.%3Cp%3EMaree%20Ellard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20strict%20dress%20code%20doesn't%20always%20mean%20sacrificing%20your%20sense%20of%20style.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20workplace%20has%20a%20business%20casual%20or%20business%20formal%20dress%20code%2C%20Ellard%20says%20you%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Btranslate%20your%20style%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20incorporating%20elements%20of%20your%20aesthetic%20into%20your%20workwear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20someone%20whose%20style%20might%20be%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froundup-tiktok-style-trends-barbiecore-goblincore-2022-12%23still-trending-gorpcore-is-for-hikers-wherever-they-are-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C