%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20foods%20can%20still%20legally%20contain%20under%200.5%20grams%20of%20trans%20fats%2C%20registered%20dietitian%20Kristin%20Gillespie%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%2C%20so%20it%20can%20be%20worth%20watching%20out%20for%20them.%20They%20typically%20appear%20in%20ingredient%20lists%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ftrans-fat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epartially%20hydrogenated%26quot%3B%20oil%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20foods%20such%20as%20margarine%2C%20pre-made%20pie%20crust%2C%20non-dairy%20coffee%20creamer%2C%20and%20packaged%20baked%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEat%20less%20sugar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20healthiest%20diet%20involves%20%26quot%3Bavoiding%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20people%20like%20to%20eat%2C%26quot%3B%20Maroon%20said%2C%20including%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Heidi%20Tissenbaum%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20professor%20in%20molecular%2C%20cell%2C%20and%20cancer%20biology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Massachusetts%20Medical%20School%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20in%20her%20research%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-you-can-do-to-live-longer-healthier-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eremoving%20added%20sugar%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20diet%20of%20roundworms%2C%20which%20are%20used%20to%20model%20human%20healthspan%2C%20was%20linked%20to%20increased%20longevity.%20It's%20thought%20this%20is%20because%20when%20the%20body%20metabolizes%20sugar%2C%20it%20produces%20byproducts%20that%20are%20associated%20with%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20diabetes%2C%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%2C%20and%20Alzheimer's%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20keep%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20stable%20to%20prevent%20wearing%20out%20the%20mechanism%20the%20pancreas%20uses%20to%20regulate%20spikes%2C%20which%20can%20increase%