s%20born%20to%20cheetahs%20in%20Kuno%2C%20how%20many%20animals%20had%20died%20till%20now%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20their%20deaths%20in%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20high%20numbers%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20asked%20whether%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20till%20now%20is%20%E2%80%9Cusual%20or%20unusual%E2%80%9D%20in%20such%20cheetah%20relocation%20projects%2C%20and%20what%20efforts%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20to%20avoid%20more%20cheetah%20deaths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply%2C%20the%20cheetahs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Ffemale-cheetah-from-namibia-dies-in-mps-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESasha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fsecond-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park-in-less-than-one-month%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthird-african-cheetah-dies-in-india-five-to-be-released-in-kuno-soon%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDaksha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Crenal%20insufficiency%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cneurological%E2%80%9D%20issues%2C%20and%20during%20a%20%E2%80%9Cviolent%20encounter%20with%20a%20male%20coalition%20during%20a%20mating%20attempt%E2%80%9D%2C%20respectively.%20The%20four%20other%20adults%20%E2%80%93%20Tejas%2C%20Suraj%2C%20Dhatri%20and%20Shaurya%20%E2%80%93%20all%20died%20due%20to%20septicemia%2C%20per%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20some%20of%20these%20causes%20vary%20from%20a%20similar%20list%20submitted%20by%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20the%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20on%20July%2020%20last%20year%2C%20also%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Per%20Choubey%E2%80%99s%20submission%2C%20while%20Sasha%20died%20due%20to%20chronic%20renal%20or%20kidney%20failure%2C%20Daksha%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%20(as%20opposed%20to%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20latest%20list%20that%20puts%20it%20to%20a%20violent%20mating%20attempt)%2C%20and%20Uday%20died%20due%20to%20cardiopulmonary%20failure%20(as%20opposed%20to%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20most%20recent%20list%20that%20lists%20the%20cause%20of%20Uday%E2%80%99s%20death%20as%20%E2%80%9Cneurological%E2%80%9D).%20Officials%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20had%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcheetah-uday-dies-of-heart-attack-triggered-by-toxin-post-mortem-reveals-101682361675687.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20April%2025%20last%20year%20that%20as%20per%20the%20preliminary%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20Uday%20died%20due%20to%20cardiopulmonary%20failure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1.jpg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1-1024x409.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22449%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20reasons%20for%20death%2C%20as%20submitted%20by%20Choubey%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20July%2020%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFour%20cheetahs%20died%20due%20to%20septicemia%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChoubey%20also%20said%20that%20Tejas%2C%20Suraj%20and%20Daksha%20died%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D.%20Yadav%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20submitted%20in%20his%20latest%20list%20that%20the%20three%20cheetahs%20died%20of%20%E2%80%9Csepticemia%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20possibly%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Ministry%20is%20admitting%20to%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221039%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2.jpg%201039w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2-300x113.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2-1024x387.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696475%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22393%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20reason%20for%20deaths%20of%20cheetahs%20as%20submitted%20by%20Union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20implementing%20Project%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20July%2016%20last%20year%20saying%20that%20all%20cheetah%20deaths%20occurred%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20any%20reports%20attributing%20the%20deaths%20to%20other%20reasons%20are%20%E2%80%9Cspeculation%20and%20hearsay%20and%20not%20based%20on%20any%20scientific%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%20This%20came%20a%20day%20after%20two%20experts%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(on%20July%2015%20last%20year)%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20were%20caused%20by%20septicaemia%2C%20an%20infection%20of%20the%20bloodstream%2C%20brought%20on%20by%20wounds%20caused%20by%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20abrasion%20of%20radio%20collars%20fitted%20on%20their%20necks%20and%20moisture%20accumulated%20under%20the%20collars.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20experts%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Suraj%E2%80%99s%20death%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpotentially%20avoidable%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20authorities%20lost%20%E2%80%9Ca%20full%20day%E2%80%9D%20in%20taking%20action%20while%20waiting%20for%20the%20post-mortem%20report%20of%20Tejas%2C%20the%20first%20cheetah%20to%20die%20of%20a%20neck%20wound%20on%20July%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%202%2C%20a%20press%20note%20released%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20forest%20department%20said%20that%20a%20monitoring%20team%20found%20Dhatri%2C%20a%20female%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20that%20morning.%20The%20animal%2C%20which%20authorities%20were%20trying%20to%20capture%20from%20the%20wild%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Surya%2C%20was%20then%20the%20sixth%20adult%20to%20die.%20In%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCCFCheetah%2Fstatus%2F1687116755548995584%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseries%20of%20tweets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20August%203%2C%20the%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%20(CCF)%20which%20has%20assisted%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20said%20that%20a%20post-mortem%20revealed%20that%20Dhatri%20died%20due%20to%20myiasis%2C%20or%20infection%20caused%20by%20fly%20larvae%20(maggots).%20As%20per%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20latest%20list%2C%20Dhatri%20died%20of%20septicemia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seventh%20death%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20recent%20so%20far%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20of%20Shaurya%2C%20a%20male%20from%20Namibia%2C%20on%20January%2016.%20Yadav%2C%20in%20his%20recent%20list%2C%20has%20also%20submitted%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20Shaurya%20too%20died%20of%20septicemia.%20The%20animal%2C%20housed%20in%20an%20enclosure%2C%20was%20treated%20for%20%E2%80%9Cweakness%E2%80%9D%20after%20it%20displayed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstaggering%20gait%E2%80%9D%2C%20officials%20had%20said.%20However%2C%20the%20animal%20died%20despite%20treatment.%20Officials%20had%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20could%20be%20ascertained%20only%20once%20the%20detailed%20post-mortem%20results%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced%20by%20the%20Ministry%20or%20the%20NTCA%20%E2%80%93%20came%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20ensure%20conservation%20and%20protection%20of%20Cheetahs%20in%20India%2C%20actions%20are%20taken%20as%20per%20scientific%20action%20plan%20prepared%20with%20inputs%20of%20leading%20Cheetah%20experts%20including%20biologists%2C%20ecologists%2C%20conservationists%20and%20managers.%20A%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20review%20progress%2C%20monitor%20and%20advise%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20introduction%20in%20consultation%20with%20international%20cheetah%20experts%2C%20as%20and%20when%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Action%20Plan%20for%20the%20introduction%20of%20Cheetah%2C%2012-14%20individuals%20per%20year%20are%20proposed%20to%20be%20brought%20from%20South%20Africa%20and%20Namibia%20or%20other%20African%20countries%20during%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20availability%20of%20animals%20and%20status%20of%20introduced%20cheetahs%2C%20Yadav%20said%20in%20his%20response%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20His%20reply%20also%20mentioned%20that%20actions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20introduce%20cheetahs%20into%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707544565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsepticemia-caused-deaths-of-four-cheetahs-union-environment-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adult%20male%20Shaurya%20that%20died%20on%20January%2016%20is%20the%20fourth%20cheetah%20to%20die%20due%20to%20septicemia%2C%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsepticemia-caused-deaths-of-four-cheetahs-union-environment-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20residents%20surviving%20off%20animal%20feed%20and%20rice%20as%20food%20dwindles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707544304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1320E%2Fproduction%2F_132605387_rtrrafahfood050224a00eac29801d15dc4e8311b3ced49092dffe4e2c0_594_4291_24151000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68239320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN%20says%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20in%20the%20territory%20are%20at%20growing%20risk%20of%20famine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A738%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68239320%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A