dians-abroad%2Fwho-was-vivek-taneja-5-facts-about-indian-origin-man-who-died-in-us-5029725%5C%22%3EVivek%20Taneja%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Virginia%2C%20and%20the%20suspect%20were%20at%20two%20sister%20Japanese%20restaurants%20on%20February%202%2C%20a%20police%20report%20said.%20He%20was%20%26quot%3Bwas%20knocked%20to%20the%20ground%20by%20the%20suspect%20and%20hit%20his%20head%20on%20the%20pavement%26quot%3B%2C%20Washington%20Posted%20cited%20a%20police%20report%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20amid%20a%20spate%20of%20attacks%20on%20and%20deaths%20of%20Indians%20and%20Indian-Americans%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaneja%2C%2041%2C%20left%20the%20restaurants%20around%202%20am%20and%20the%20fight%20broke%20out%20on%20a%20nearby%20street%2C%20the%20police%20report%20said%20without%20describing%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20dispute.%20He%20lost%20consciousness%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20when%20the%20cops%20arrived%2C%20they%20found%20him%20with%20life%20threatening%20injuries%20and%20rushed%20him%20to%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20died%20from%20the%20injuries%20at%20the%20hospital%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20suspects%20image%20shared%20by%20the%20police%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20suspects%20image%20shared%20by%20the%20police%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F05d2mjig_vivek-taneja-killer_625x300_10_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect's%20image%20shared%20by%20the%20police%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20is%20on%20for%20the%20suspect%20who%20was%20seen%20on%20CCTV.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20offered%20a%20%2425%2C000%20reward%20for%20anyone%20who%20provides%20information%20that%20leads%20to%20his%20arrest%20and%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaneja%20was%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Dynamo%20Technologies%2C%20a%20technology%20solutions%20and%20analytics%20product%20provider%20to%20the%20US%20government.%20He%20was%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20company%20and%20led%20its%20strategic%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20partnership%20initiatives%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20an%20Indian%20student%20was%20left%20bleeding%20from%20his%20nose%20and%20mouth%20after%20he%20was%20attacked%20by%20robbers%20in%20Chicago.%20Syed%20Mazahir%20Ali%2C%20who%20family%20lives%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20was%20seen%20in%20a%20video%20pleading%20for%20help%20following%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20Indian-origin%20students%20were%20reported%20dead%20in%20the%20US%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESameer%20Kamath%2C%20an%20Indian-American%20studying%20at%20Purdue%20University%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20a%20nature%20reserve%20this%20week.%20Authorities%20said%20he%20died%20from%20a%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound%20to%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20Reddy%20Beniger%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20student%20who%20held%20an%20American%20passport%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20last%20week%2C%20but%20authorities%20had%20ruled%20out%20any%20foul%20play.%20Another%20student%2C%20Neel%20Acharya%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20Purdue%20University%20campus%20earlier%20that%20week%2C%20hours%20after%20his%20mother%20had%20reported%20him%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Saini%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20student%20from%20Haryana%2C%20was%20hammered%20to%20death%20by%20a%20homeless%20man%20in%20Georgia's%20Lithonia%20on%20January%2016.%20Akul%20Dhawan%2C%20another%20Indian%20student%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20outside%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20wake%20of%20the%20deaths%2C%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20reassured%20that%20the%20US%20is%20committed%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20remains%20safe%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20heart%20always%20is%20t