20small%20parties%20and%20other%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20Muslim%20League%20is%20the%20single-largest%20party%20in%20the%20country%20today%20after%20the%20elections%20and%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20bring%20this%20country%20out%20of%20the%20whirlpool%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20told%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20has%20got%20the%20mandate%2C%20whether%20independents%20or%20parties%2C%20we%20respect%20the%20mandate%20they%20have%20got%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20invite%20them%20to%20sit%20with%20us%20and%20help%20this%20wounded%20nation%20get%20back%20on%20its%20feet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%2C%2074%2C%20a%20three-time%20former%20premier%2C%20returned%20from%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20late%20last%20year%2C%20having%20contested%20the%20last%20election%20from%20a%20jail%20cell%20on%20a%20graft%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20considered%20the%20front-runner%20to%20lead%20the%20country%2C%20having%20buried%20a%20long-running%20feud%20with%20the%20powerful%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20said%20his%20party%20would%20have%20preferred%20to%20win%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20own%20but%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20that%20would%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20others%2C%20including%20former%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20of%20PPP%2C%20to%20open%20negotiations%20as%20early%20as%20Friday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20reaction%2C%20a%20senior%20aide%20of%20Khan%20said%20leaders%20of%20his%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%20would%20hold%20talks%20among%20themselves%20and%20also%20meet%20Khan%20in%20jail%20on%20Saturday%20to%20discuss%20the%20results%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20of%20the%20vote%20have%20been%20unusually%20delayed%2C%20which%20the%20caretaker%20government%20ascribed%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20phone%20services%20-%20a%20security%20measure%20ahead%20of%20Thursday's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20members%20cannot%20form%20a%20government%20on%20their%20own%20under%20Pakistan's%20complex%20election%20system%20which%20also%20includes%20reserved%20seats%20that%20will%20be%20allotted%20to%20parties%20based%20on%20their%20winnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20independent%20members%20have%20the%20option%20to%20join%20any%20party%20after%20the%20elections.%20Khan's%20party%20was%20barred%20from%20the%20election%2C%20so%20his%20supporters%20contested%20as%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20For%20Coalition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20timely%20announcement%20of%20the%20results%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20smooth%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20government%2C%20will%20reduce%20policy%20and%20political%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody's%20Investors%20Service%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20country%20that%20is%20facing%20very%20challenging%20macroeconomic%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20the%20announcement%20of%20results%20was%20unusual%20for%20elections%20in%20Pakistan.%20Karachi's%20stock%20index%20and%20Pakistan's%20sovereign%20bonds%20fell%20because%20of%20the%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%26quot%3Binternet%20issue%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20delay%2C%20Zafar%20Iqbal%2C%20special%20secretary%20at%20the%20election%20commission%2C%20said%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20electoral%20battle%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20between%20candidates%20backed%20by%20Khan%2C%20whose%20PTI%20won%20the%20last%20national%20election%2C%20and%20the%20PML-N.%20Khan%20believes%20the%20powerful%20military%20is%20behind%20a%20crackdown%20to%20hound%20his%20party%20out%20of%20existence%2C%20while%20analysts%20and%20opponents%20say%20Sharif%20is%20being%20backed%20by%20the%20generals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20has%20dominated%20the%20nuclear-armed%20country%20either%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20in%20its%2076%20years%20of%20independence%20from%20Britain%20but%20for%20several%20years%20it%20has%20maintained%20it%20does%20not%20interfere%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20a%20coalition%20government%20will%20struggle%20to%20tackle%20multiple%20challenges%20-%20foremost%20being%20seeking%20a%20new%20bailout%20programme%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20after%20the%20current%20arrangement%20expires%20in%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20government%20%26quot%3Bwould%20probably%20be%20unstable%2C%20weak%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20big%20loser%20...%20will%20be%20the%20army%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Marvin%20Weinbaum%2C%20Director%20of%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan%20Studies%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%20Institute%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20army%20really%20has%20staked%20its%20reputation%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver%20this%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20was%20expected%20to%20help%20resolve%20the%20crises%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20but%20a%20fractured%20verdict%20%26quot%3Bcould%20very%20well%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20even%20deeper%20exposure%20to%20forces%20which%20would%20create%20instability%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20troops%20were%20deployed%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20at%20polling%20stations%20across%20the%20country%20for%20the%20voting%20on%20Thursday.%20Borders%20with%20Iran%20and%20Afghanistan%20were%20temporarily%20closed%20as%20security%20was%20stepped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20heightened%20security%2C%2028%20people%2C%20including%20two%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20in%2056%20attacks%20including%20bomb%20and%20grenade%20blasts%20and%20shootings%20by%20militants%2C%20the%20Interior%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20said%20it%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20%26quot%3Btimely%2C%20complete%20election%20results%26quot%3B%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20reflecting%20the%20will%20of%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20prepared%20to%20work%20with%20the%20next%20Pakistani%20government%2C%20regardless%20of%20political%20party%2C%20to%20advance%20our%20shared%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20State%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20Sharif%20claimed%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707496380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fpquqk9m_nawaz-sharif_625x300_09_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-claims-victory-in-pakistan-elections-5026579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20on%20Friday%20claimed%20victory%20in%20national%20elections%2C%20saying%20that%20his%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20party%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20results.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-claims-victory-in-pakistan-elections-5026579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-claims-victory-in-pakistan-elections-5026579%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-claims-victory-in-pakistan-elections-5026579%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vedanta%20Resources%20makes%20upfront%20payment%20of%20%24779%20mn%20to%20bondholders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707496064000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-12%2F29%2Ffull%2F1609235533-0889.jpg%22%2C%22originID