e%20situation%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SPG%20security%20team%20struck%20me%2C%20causing%20me%20to%20fall%20to%20the%20ground.%20Mr.%20Rao%20was%20preparing%20to%20enter%20his%20car%20when%20I%20cried%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Rao%2C%20your%20security%20personnel%20are%20assaulting%20me.%26quot%3B%20Without%20hesitation%2C%20Rao%20emerged%20from%20the%20car%20and%20assured%20me%20that%20no%20harm%20would%20come%20to%20me.%20I%20rose%20to%20my%20feet%2C%20thrust%20my%20microphone%20towards%20him%2C%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWill%20you%20resign%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20responded%20forcefully%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20does%20not%20arise.%26quot%3B%20With%20that%2C%20I%20had%20my%20exclusive%20headline%2C%20and%20his%20convoy%20departed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Unique%20Demeanour%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20young%20reporter%20like%20myself%2C%20it%20was%20a%20significant%20scoop.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20it%20dominated%20the%20front%20pages%20of%20all%20the%20newspapers.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20television%20news%20was%20still%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20and%20reporters%20such%20as%20myself%20were%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bbite%20collectors%26quot%3B.%20While%20we%20were%20not%20yet%20treated%20as%20celebrities%2C%20the%20media%20landscape%20was%20relatively%20free%2C%20affording%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pose%20questions%20to%20figures%20of%20political%20importance%2C%20including%20prime%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%2C%20however%2C%20was%20somewhat%20unique%20in%20his%20demeanour%2C%20not%20particularly%20camera-friendly.%20On%20any%20other%20occasion%2C%20he%20might%20have%20evaded%20my%20question.%20Yet%2C%20upon%20witnessing%20me%20being%20accosted%20by%20his%20security%20detail%2C%20he%20graciously%20obliged%20with%20his%20statement.%20Even%20now%2C%20three%20decades%20later%2C%20that%20image%20of%20him%20remains%20etched%20in%20my%20memory.%20And%20today%2C%20as%20he%20is%20posthumously%20honoured%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20I%20fondly%20recollect%20that%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EManmohan%20Singh%20%26amp%3B%20Rao%3A%20A%20Formidable%20Duo%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarsimha%20Rao%20was%2C%20in%20the%20truest%20sense%2C%20an%20accidental%20Prime%20Minister.%20Had%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20not%20been%20assassinated%20midway%20through%20the%201991%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Rao%20might%20have%20faded%20into%20political%20obscurity.%20Initially%20denied%20a%20ticket%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20he%20had%20relocated%20his%20base%20to%20Hyderabad.%20However%2C%20following%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20death%2C%20he%20not%20only%20ascended%20to%20the%20presidency%20of%20the%20party%20but%20also%20later%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20was%20not%20a%20charismatic%20mass%20leader%20by%20any%20means%3B%20the%20then%20tall%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Arjun%20Singh%20boasted%20stronger%20claims%20to%20the%20premiership.%20Yet%2C%20Rao%2C%20perceived%20as%20the%20least%20contentious%20choice%20among%20them%2C%20emerged%20as%20the%20preferred%20candidate%20among%20Congress%20MPs.%20India%20was%20grappling%20with%20severe%20economic%20challenges%2C%20necessitating%20urgent%20attention.%20Rao's%20astuteness%20lay%20in%20appointing%20a%20professional%20economist%20like%20Manmohan%20Singh%20as%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20eschewing%20the%20selection%20of%20a%20politician.%20Recognising%20the%20imperative%20to%20insulate%20the%20economy%20from%20political%20machinations%2C%20Rao%20bluntly%20informed%20Singh%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20manage%20the%20economy%2C%20I%20will%20manage%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EDrivers%20Of%20Growth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao's%20decision%20to%20appoint%20Manmohan%20Singh%20proved%20pivotal%20in%20India's%20political%20trajectory.%20His%20keen%20understanding%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20led%20him%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20socialist%20model%20of%20development%20had%20failed%2C%20and%20perpetuating%20it%20would%20mean%20more%20misery%20for%20the%20people.%20Despite%20widespread%20scepticism%20towards%20market%20economies%20and%20global%20economic%20institutions%2C%20Rao%20boldly%20pursued%20economic%20liberalisation%2C%20dismantling%20bureaucratic%20impediments%20and%20initiating%20reforms%20to%20attract%20foreign%20investment.%20His%20actions%20were%20courageous%2C%20and%20seemingly%20unpopular.%20There%20was%20a%20powerful%20club%20of%20opinion%20makers%2C%20trained%20as%20they%20were%20in%20Left-of-the-Centre%20ideology%2C%20ever%20ready%20to%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20going%20against%20the%20path%20travelled%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20they%20were%20instrumental%20in%20steering%20the%20country%20towards%20economic%20growth.%20Today%2C%20as%20India%20emerges%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%20economies%20and%20prepares%20to%20claim%20the%20mantle%20of%20the%20third-largest%20economy%2C%20credit%20must%20be%20accorded%20to%20the%20formidable%20duo%20of%20Rao%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20estimation%2C%20Rao%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20underestimated%20Prime%20Ministers%20in%20Indian%20history.%20However%2C%20while%20celebrating%20his%20accomplishments%2C%20one%20cannot%20ignore%20his%20failures.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Rao%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20restoring%20stability%20to%20regions%20plagued%20by%20violence%2C%20such%20as%20Punjab%20and%20Kashmir.%20Upon%20assuming%20office%2C%20both%20states%20were%20engulfed%20in%20turmoil%3B%20by%20the%20time%20he%20departed%2C%20the%20situation%20had%20markedly%20improved.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20tactics%20he%20used%20to%20stay%20in%20power%20and%20the%20political%20scandals%20that%20followed%20tarnished%20his%20legacy.%20Yet%2C%20Rao's%20erudition%2C%20multilingualism%2C%20and%20bold%20leadership%20continue%20to%20command%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EOn%20Charan%20Singh%20%26amp%3B%20Political%20Speculation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20contribution%20of%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-ratna-for-former-pms-charan-singh-pv-narasimha-rao-5023954%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%2C%20Charan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20also%20been%20posthumously%20awarded%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20alongside%20Rao%2C%20mostly%20remains%20outside%20the%20realm%20of%20governance%20and%20is%20more%20associated%20with%20providing%20a%20platform%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhonour-to-farmers-yogi-adityanath-on-bharat-ratna-for-ex-pm-chaudhary-charan-singh-5024776%5C%22%3Ebackward%20politics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchaudhary-charan-singh-bharat-ratna-jayant-chaudhary-rld-bjp-alliance-dil-jeet-liya-rld-leader-as-pm-announces-bharat-ratna-for-charan-singh-5024116%5C%22%3ECharan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E's%20tenure%20was%20brief%2C%20and%20he%20never%20faced%20Parliament%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20A%20staunch%20advocate%20for%20farmers'%20rights%20and%20a%20vocal%20opponent%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20Charan%20Singh's%20legacy%20is%20viewed%20through%20a%20political%20lens.%20The%20Bharat%20Ratna%20awarded%20to%20him%2C%20announced%20amidst%20speculation%20regarding%20his%20grandson's%20political%20affiliations%2C%20may%20carry%20political%20implications.%20As%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20in%20Bihar%2C%20whose%20posthumous%20honour%20led%20to%20a%20political%20realignment%2C%20Charan%20Singh's%20award%20sparks%20similar%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-ratna-for-ms-swaminathan-5-facts-about-father-of-green-revolution-5024773%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2520on%2Cachieve%2520self%252Dreliance%2520in%2520agriculture.%5C%22%3EM.S.%20Swaminathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20undoubtedly%20stands%20among%20India's%20greatest%20luminaries.%20Dubbed%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20he%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20making%20India%20self-sufficient%20in%20food%20grain%20production.%20Despite%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri's%20initial%20initiative%2C%20it%20was%20Swaminathan%20who%20translated%20the%20vision%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20seeking%20to%20expand%20its%20footprint%20in%20South%20India%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20conferred%20upon%20Swaminathan%20and%20Rao%2C%20the%20latter%20being%20a%20Telugu%20leader%2C%20could%20be%20interpreted%20as%20yet%20another%20attempt%20to%20bolster%20its%20presence%20south%20of%20the%20Vindhyas.%20However%2C%20given%20the%20BJP's%20limited%20influence%20in%20states%20like%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20such%20honours%20on%20the%20party's%20fortunes%20remains%20uncertain%20in%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707482280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqmvi387g_pv-narasimha-rao_625x300_09_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frichly-deserved-bharat-ratna-for-indias-accidental-prime-minister-pv-narasimha-rao-5025452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rao%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20underestimated%20Prime%20Ministers%20in%20Indian%20history.%20Despite%20widespread%20scepticism%2C%20he%20boldly%20pursued%20economic%20liberalisation%2C%20dismantling%20bureaucratic%20impediments%20and%20initiating%20reforms%20to%20attract%20foreign%20investment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frichly-deserved-bharat-ratna-for-indias-accidental-prime-minister-pv-narasimha-rao-5025452%22%2C%2