0Fight%20for%20Equality%20Led%20to%20the%20IAF%20Giving%20Permanent%20Commission%20to%20Female%20Officers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Garima%20Sachdeva%20would%20see%20her%20father%20%E2%80%93%20a%20senior%20rank%20Air%20Force%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20dressed%20up%20in%20the%20blue%20uniform%20every%20morning%2C%20proudly%20placing%20a%20hat%20on%20his%20head.%20He%20would%20wear%20his%20overalls%20and%20flying%20boots%2C%20marching%20to%20his%20workplace%20to%20safeguard%20the%20country%20from%20all%20aerial%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20did%20not%20know%20as%20a%20child%20that%20there%20were%20women%20in%20the%20same%20blue%20uniform%20doing%20the%20exact%20same%20work%20as%20well.%20Despite%20flying%20the%20mean%20machines%20in%20the%20Indian%20skies%20and%20conducting%20all%20the%20ground%20duties%2C%20they%20were%20still%20not%20getting%20what%20I%20saw%20my%20dad%20get%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garima%2C%20now%2032%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20opportunity%20to%20be%20in%20service%20for%20as%20many%20years%20as%20the%20male%20officers%20and%20retirement%20benefits%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20were%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20her%20father%20%E2%80%98retired%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20rank%20of%20Air%20Marshal%20after%20serving%20for%20a%20good%2040%20years%2C%20whereas%20women%20officers%20were%20%E2%80%98released%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20service%20only%20after%2010-14%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20the%20ropes%20of%20gender%20inequality%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20Garima%2C%20who%20practices%20law%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20decided%20to%20fight%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20along%20with%20a%20large%20team%20of%20lawyers.%20They%20were%20led%20by%20Rekha%20Palli%20%5Bnow%20sitting%20Judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%5D%2C%20and%20her%20competent%20team%20of%20f