3Cp%3EAman%20Rai%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineering%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20is%20a%20passionate%20runner%20with%20many%20ultra-marathons%20under%20his%20belt.%20Upon%20starting%20his%20career%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20juggle%20his%20job%20responsibilities%20with%20regular%20gym%20visits%20for%20strength%20training%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20runners.%20Residing%20in%20a%20rented%20accommodation%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20limited%20equipment%20at%20his%20disposal%20at%20home%20fell%20short%20of%20adequately%20supporting%20his%20training%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Dani%20also%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20find%20time%20to%20head%20to%20the%20gym%20due%20to%20long%20work%20hours.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rohit%20Patel%20and%20Amal%20George%2C%20who%20were%20studying%20robotics%2C%20spent%20hours%20building%20solutions%20for%20everyday%20problems%2C%20and%20were%20keen%20on%20solving%20this%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20really%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20no%20single%20equipment%20that%20could%20replicate%20the%20entire%20gym%20at%20home.%20They%20discovered%20that%20home%20gym%20equipment%20was%20big%2C%20costly%2C%20and%20demanded%20ample%20space.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20accurately%20monitor%20their%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20have%20to%20keep%20buying%20different%20weights%20and%20bars%20to%20train%20at%20home.%20This%20occupies%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20especially%20in%20rented%20spaces%20and%20small%20apartments.%20It%20also%20becomes%20bulky%20and%20unsafe.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20new%20digital-weights%20technology%20emerged.%20Amal%20and%20Rohit%2C%20robotics%20graduates%2C%20explored%20creating%20a%20similar%20system.%20They%20began%20prototyping%2C%20aiming%20to%20replace%20physical%20weights%20with%20digital%20ones%20using%20motors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20replicate%20the%20same%20types%20of%20resistance%20that%20a%20physical%20weight%20provides%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20motor%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20four%20of%20them%20worked%20on%20building%20prototypes%2C%20investing%20almost%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20of%20their%20own%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Aroleap%20X%20comes%20with%20over%20150%20exercises%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-272x182.jpg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340985%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Aroleap%20X%20comes%20with%20over%20150%20exercises.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20they%20incorporated%20their%20company%20by%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Aroleap%20Fitness%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99.%20Amid%20the%20pandemic%2C%20like%20most%20people%2C%20the%20founders%20headed%20home.%20Aman%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Anurag%20hail%20from%20Bhilai%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20have%20known%20each%20other%20since%20school.%20So%20they%20were%20able%20to%20continue%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298698%2Fflexnest-home-gym-equipment-fitness-startup-earns-millions-no-vc-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ER%26amp%3BD%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20winter%20of%202020%2C%20with%20their%20first%20prototype%20in%20hand%2C%20they%20initiated%20their%20first%20round%20of%20trials%20by%20inviting%20friends%20from%20school%20over.%20They%20filmed%20a%20video%20showcasing%20their%20product%20and%20commenced%20sharing%20it%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20get%20people%20interested%20in%20the%20product%2C%20we%20started%20by%20offering%20monthly%20subscriptions%2C%20priced%20equal%20to%20a%20premium%20gym%20membership.%20We%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20and%20once%20back%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20we%20sent%20our%20prototypes%20to%20a%20few%20people%20who%20seemed%20very%20interested%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20first%20customers%20tried%20the%20product%20for%20four%20to%20six%20months%20and%20offered%20their%20feedback%20to%20the%20founders.%20Based%20on%20the%20feedback%2C%20the%20engineers%20made%20changes%20to%20the%20product.%20Once%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20the%20product%2C%20they%20encountered%20the%20big%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20try%20their%20luck%2C%20Rohit%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20Nithin%20Kamath%2C%20CEO%20of%20Zerodha.%20Aman%20states%20that%20Nithin%20came%20to%20their%20apartment%20in%20J%20P%20Nagar%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20tried%20the%20prototype.%20Impressed%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20bet%20on%20them%20and%20become%20their%20first%20angel%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20found%20three%20other%20investors%20and%20raised%20their%20seed%20capital%20in%20October%202021.%20Then%2C%20they%20set%20up%20a%20small%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20began%20selling%20Aroleap%20X%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20home%20gym%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Aroleap%20(%40aroleap)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAroleap%20X%20is%20a%20compact%2C%20wall-mounted%20smart%20exercise%20machine%20that%20uses%20motor-powered%20electromagnetic%20resistances%20to%20provide%20a%20data-driven%20workout.%20The%20device%20takes%20up%204%20feet%20x%202%20feet%20space%2C%20which%20is%20equivalent%20to%20a%20vertically%20wall-mounted%2055%20inch%20LED%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20patented%20digital-weights%20technology%20was%20built%20in-house%20and%20comes%20with%20fitness%20content%20to%20support%20workouts.%20The%20machine%20uses%20a%20motor%20to%20simulate%20the%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20pull%20the%20rope%20on%20the%20device%2C%20it%20generates%20resistance.%20Our%20device%20works%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322864%2Fkochi-aathira-sethumadhavan-pcos-weight-loss-healthy-diet-nutrition-sustainable-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20trainer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tells%20you%20when%20to%20reduce%20or%20increase%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20can%20be%20used%20to%20do%20everything%20that%20you%20do%20at%20a%20gym%2C%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20technology%20has%20condensed%20all%20different%20weight%20stacks%20into%20a%20single%20motor.%20We%20have%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20motor-controlled%20technology.%20Our%20motor%20provides%20resistance%20from%202%20kg%20to%2075%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20150%20exercises%20can%20be%20done%20using%20the%20machine%2C%20and%20every%20muscle%20group%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20body%20can%20be%20targeted.%20AI-powered%20training%20sessions%20track%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20progress%20and%20suggest%20better%20methods%20of%20working%20out%2C%20while%20giving%20real-time%20tracking%20and%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20offers%20goal-based%20workout%20programmes%2C%20designed%20by%20professional%20fitness%20trainers.%20From%20building%20muscle%20and%20weight%20training%20to%20becoming%20a%20better%20runner%2C%20the%20machine%20has%20something%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20comes%20with%20two%20arms%2C%20which%20can%20be%20adjusted%