0are%20available%20abroad%2C%20like%20Tonal%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20this%20is%20the%20only%20one%20in%20India%2C%20manufactured%20completely%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshat%20Jalan%20from%20Gurugram%20has%20been%20using%20the%20Aroleap%20X%20for%20around%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20He%20says%20that%20this%20equipment%20helps%20him%20workout%20diligently%20and%20that%20it%20provides%20everything%20needed%20for%20an%20efficient%20workout%20without%20occupying%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20time%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20regularly.%20I%20tried%20getting%20a%20bunch%20of%20equipment%20to%20workout%20at%20home%20but%20the%20result%20was%20suboptimal.%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20do%20all%20the%20exercises%20I%20would%20normally%20do%20at%20the%20gym.%20Aroleap%20provides%20a%20holistic%20workout%20and%20is%20equivalent%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20for%20me.%20It%20is%20convenient%2C%20tracks%20data%2C%20and%20helps%20you%20scientifically%20plan%20your%20routines%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akshat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAroleap%20is%20sold%20at%20Rs%201.69%20lakh%20through%20their%20website%20and%20on%20Amazon.%20They%20have%20sold%20over%20300%20home%20gyms%2C%20so%20far%2C%20across%2020%20cities%2C%20and%20had%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203.5%20crore%20in%20the%20year%202023-24.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20also%20been%20selling%20their%20product%20in%20the%20B2B%20space%20to%20hotels%2C%20co-working%20spaces%2C%20and%20physiotherapy%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoping%20to%20expand%20to%20the%20international%20market%20soon%2C%20Aman%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297548%2Fborderline-anorexic-mumbai-woman-finds-healthy-fitness-lifestyle-routine-diet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20simple%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20accessible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bh